title: 181. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden's Judge, Colleges Offering Therapy & U.S. Travel Restrictions
itunes:title: 181. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden's Judge, Colleges Offering Therapy & U.S. Travel Restrictions
description: In today's episode, Andy and DJ talk about Joe Biden's nomination of the judge in the Ghislaine Maxwell trial, college & universities offering therapy for students affected by the "racist" Rittenhouse verdict and the new travel restriction imposed by the U.S. government over the new COVID-19 variant.
